{"tid":2198263,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"金融才俊租北角尚譽193呎海景戶 呎租76元","createTime":"2020-09-11T08:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T10:21:55.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b4728f721139d6b916eeda9ef8029c2821ae03","tid":2198263,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:31:14.000Z","msg":"香港置業北角城市花園分行首席分區董事林文奇表示，北角尚譽臨近維港，而且鄰近港鐵站，交通方便，吸引不少外區客進駐。該行剛促成的一宗尚譽海景單位租務成交，外區客斥1.47萬元承租，實用租約76元，屬市價成交。<br />\n<br />\n上述單位為尚譽高層A室，望海景，開放式間隔，實用面積約193平方呎。林文奇指，業主以約1.53萬元放租約4個月後吸引外區客洽詢，雙方議價後減價600元，以1.47萬元租出，實用呎租約76元，減幅約4%。據悉，新租客為一名金融才俊，心儀單位旺中帶靜，故睇樓1次後火速決定承租。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，原業主於2018年11月以約558.46萬元購入上述單位，現享回報逾3厘。"},{"pid":"660d61a24cd2b745b295032687391fc19cb91ff4","tid":2198263,"uid":134997,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:32:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69c2a4105fd1f6819335b555a450ad0ab2b2adb3","tid":2198263,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:33:08.000Z","msg":"華匯系啲人?"},{"pid":"0f4c18ebadce0292cd3ae536378d64c6b07ea740","tid":2198263,"uid":75778,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:34:39.000Z","msg":"擺明拎嚟有時做嘢夜咗 <br />\n係到訓<br />\n或食女用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aabf4553c9b14f59469a74ab8704004dd9eeb419","tid":2198263,"uid":154258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"萬五蚊租劏房<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解唔租酒店？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4722a833bd308d0d98abf5dbbcacae63c4a60a2b","tid":2198263,"uid":522,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aabf4553c9b14f59469a74ab8704004dd9eeb419","tid":2198263,"uid":154258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"萬五蚊租劏房<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" 